DESCRIPTION {
    Oh, there comes a support request from the forgetful Heidi, one of our animal keepers:
    
   <i> « I urgently need to identify the youngest bear's food bowl. But I don't know what his name is anymore. Can you help me? » </i>
}

ANSWER {
    SELECT name, birthdate FROM zoo_animal WHERE birthdate = (SELECT MAX(birthdate) FROM zoo_animal WHERE type = 'bear');
}

